This paper belongs to the field of optimization algorithms, which is a subfield of computer science. The paper specifically focuses on a hybrid algorithm that combines artificial bee colony (ABC) algorithm with genetic algorithm (GA) for optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which deals with optimization algorithms and their applications. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), as these sub-categories also cover optimization algorithms and their applications in various fields.
